---
title: Zesty Chicken Tenders With Smashed Broccoli and Lemon Mayo
description: Zesty spiced chicken tenders get the perfect internet-famous side of smashed broccoli, made crispy with lacy edges of Parmesan! Dip and dunk the chicken, potatoes and broccoli in the creamy, dreamy lemon mayo!

